<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.9.1">
<l>colluvaṉ coṟporuḷ tāṉavai yāyccuvai yūṟoli nāṟṟamun tōṟṟamumāy</l>
<l>nallaraṉ nāraṇaṉ nāṉmuka ṉukkiṭan tāṉtaṭañ cūḻntaḻa kāyakacci</l>
<l>pallavaṉ villava ṉeṉṟula kilpala rāyppala vēntarva ṇaṅkukaḻal</l>
<l>pallavaṉ mallaiyar kōṉpaṇin tapara mēccura viṇṇaka ramatuvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In fair Kacci encircled by ponds, the place of good Hara, four-faced [Brahmā],</l>
<l>And Nāraṇa, who became the speaker and the meaning of words,</l>
<l rend="indent">and who became taste, touch, sound, scent, and sight,</l>
<l>Is Paramēccura Viṇṇakaram where bowed the king of those of Mallai,</l>
<l rend="indent">Pallavaṉ whose feet many kings revered,</l>
<l>[They] being many in the world called Pallavas</l>
<l rend="indent">and the [Cēras] with a bow-banner.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
